<a class="right flag" rel="nofollow" id="flag_link81027" title="Flag this answer as inappropriate." href="/flagged/new?resource_id=81027&amp;resource_type=CommunityAnswer&amp;return_url=%2Fquestions%2F180179-what-would-people-think-about-someone%2Fanswers%2F81027-i-would-say-that-it">flag</a>
</div>
