<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/174626-is-it-about-one-s-right-to-decide-when-to">Is it about one&#39;s right to decide when to die?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_174626'><a id="like_count_community_question_174626" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/174626?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">11 likes</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F20696006-being-mortal">like</a></span>

