<div class='allCommunityAnswers'>
<div class='communityAnswer'>
<div class='communityAnswerBody'>
<div class='answererUserIcon'>
<a class="leftAlignedImage userPhoto" href="/user/show/33249234-mrs-danvers"><img alt="" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/users/1405979828i/33249234._UX100_CR0,0,100,100_.jpg" /></a>
</div>
<div class='communityAnswerTextContainer'>
<span class='communityAnswererName'>
<a href="/user/show/33249234-mrs-danvers">Mrs. Danvers</a>
</span>
<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">It&apos;s about what matters as we reach the end of life and what we as individuals, as a community, and as recipients of medical care can do to be sure th<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">It's about what matters as we reach the end of life and what we as individuals, as a community, and as recipients of medical care can do to be sure that we honor what matters most to the aging and/or dying person. <a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
</div>
